    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? This car is an absolute gem and has been my total pride and joy. I\u2019ve kept it in truly mint condition\u2014it's been babied, garage-kept, and looks stunning inside and out. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh feel! I'm honestly sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019ll make the next owner so happy. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 is a mechanical masterpiece, featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission delivers tactile engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. This example has undergone extensive preventative maintenance, including documented rod bearing replacement, a comprehensive Beisan Systems VANOS overhaul, and rear subframe reinforcement. The chassis remains rigid and the suspension geometry is strictly factory-spec, offering the pure, analog feedback these M-cars are known for. With immaculate original finish and a pristine interior, this is a turn-key investment for the serious enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
