      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every aspect of this specimen, from its flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior, reflects a history of meticulous care and climate-controlled storage. Mechanically superior and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, it offers a rare opportunity for the sophisticated collector to acquire a vehicle of unparalleled integrity. Detailed service records accompany the sale, confirming a legacy of preventative maintenance and absolute mechanical excellence.",
      "price": 47500.0,
